    {
      "name": "Fuel Logs",
      "description": "logged_at: ISO 8601 datetime, no future dates allowed.\n\nEither fuel_quantity or total_cost can be omitted — the server computes the missing field from the other two.\n  • Provide qty → total is computed (qty × price)\n  • Provide total → qty is computed (total ÷ price)\n\nResponse includes computed fields: km_since_last, fuel_efficiency (km/L).",
